These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
House: modern, wooden, colonial, cottage
Beverage: mirinda, soy-milk, coffee, iced-tea
1. Beverage:soy-milk is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1
2. House:modern == Beverage:iced-tea##1
3. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Beverage:mirinda##1
4. House:wooden is on the left of Beverage:iced-tea##1
5. House:cottage is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| House          | cottage | colonial | wooden | modern   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | mirinda     | coffee   | iced-tea |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Food: onion, pear, pineapple, lime
Game: billiard, monopoly, bridge, canasta
1. Food:lime == Game:monopoly##1
2. Food:onion is on the far right##1
3. Food:pear is on the right of Food:lime##1
4. Food:lime is on the right of Game:bridge##1
5. Game:monopoly is on the left of Game:billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | pineapple | lime | pear | onion    |
| Game   | bridge    | monopoly      | billiard | canasta |

