2. Transport:tram == Flower:azalea##1
3. Flower:rose is on the far right##1
4. Flower:daffodil is on the right of Transport:airplane##1
5. Transport:jet-ski is on the left of Flower:rose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Transport         | tram | airplane | jet-ski   | motorbike |
| Flower   | azalea   | bellflower | daffodil | rose         |

